    caption: [Direct repair of alkylated bases by AlkB. The AlkB protein is an (cid:2)-ketoglutarate-Fe2(cid:3)–dependent hydroxylase (see Box 4–3). It cata- lyzes the oxidative demethylation of 1-methyladenine and 3-methylcytosine residues. H2C O (cid:3) H(cid:3)],
