    caption: [The contribution of independent assortment to genetic diversity. In this example, the chromosomes have already been repli- cated to create two pairs of sister chromatids for two chromosomes. Blue and red distinguish the sister chromatids of each pair. One gene on each chromosome is highlighted, with different alleles (A or a, B or b) in],
